natural_language: Which instructors from the Cybernetics department have a salary greater than 80,000?
sql_query: SELECT name FROM instructor WHERE dept_name = 'Cybernetics' AND salary > 80000;

natural_language: What are the titles and course IDs of the Mechanical Engineering courses that have 3 credits?
sql_query: SELECT course_id, title FROM course WHERE credits = 3 AND dept_name = 'Mech. Eng.';
